posts.text:
Last week, I met with leaders from
@KYCreditUnions. I like the community-focused approach they bring to banking.

I'm cosponsoring H.R. 507, the Veterans Member Business Loan Act, to exclude credit union financing for veteran-owned businesses from the artificial caps on lending.

